article.headline: Rogers' 19 lead American over Siena 78-58

images.name: Siena Saints vs. American Eagles: Full Highlights
images.caption: Siena Saints vs. American Eagles: Full Highlights

article.story: WASHINGTON, D.C. -- — Matt Rogers' 19 points helped American defeat Siena 78-58 on Monday night. Rogers added four steals for the Eagles (1-2). Geoff Sprouse was 6 of 10 shooting (4 for 8 from 3-point range) to add 16 points. Matt Mayock shot 4 for 8, including 2 for 5 from beyond the arc to finish with 10 points. The Saints (1-2) were led by Zek Tekin, who recorded 18 points. Mason Courtney added 10 points and two steals for Siena. In addition, Michael Evbagharu finished with six points. NEXT UP American's next game is Thursday against NJIT at home. Siena takes on Central Michigan on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
